videos.headline: Kansas QB Bender finds Johnson Jr. for 31-yard TD
videos.description: Peyton Bender connects with a wide-open Kerr Johnson Jr. on a 31-yard touchdown pass to take the lead over Central Michigan.

videos.headline: Kansas RB Williams Jr. 20-yard TD run
videos.description: Kansas running back Pooka Williams Jr. navigates his way through the Central Michigan defense for a 20-yard touchdown run,

videos.headline: Kansas defense comes up with big INT
videos.description: Joe Dineen Jr. leaps to pick off Tony Poljan on the Kansas 48-yard line, giving possession back to the Jayhawks.
